{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","text":"MLNMapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"mapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"annotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotation","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)UIControl","text":"UIControl","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"control","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"mapView","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The map view containing the specified annotation.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"annotation","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The annotation whose accessory view was tapped."}]}]},{"name":"control","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The control that was tapped."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In a standard callout view, accessory views contain custom content and are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"positioned on either side of the annotation title text. If an accessory view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you specify is a descendant of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIControl"},{"type":"text","text":" class, the map view calls this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method as a convenience whenever the user taps your view. You can use this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method to respond to taps and perform any actions associated with that control."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example, if your control displays additional information about the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation, you could use this method to present a modal panel with that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your custom accessory views are not descendants of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIControl"},{"type":"text","text":" class,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the map view does not call this method. If the annotation has a custom callout"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view via the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:"},{"type":"text","text":" method, you can specify the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"custom accessory views using the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"leftAccessoryView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"rightAccessoryView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" properties.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Related examples","anchor":"Related-examples","level":4},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to trigger an action when the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"standard callout bubble’s accessory control is tapped.","type":"text"}]}]}],"sections":[],"identifi